## System Overview

**Configuration:** 9.4.6 Dolby Atmos
- **LCR:** 3× DIYSG Titan-815LX (on stage, behind 170" AT screen)
- **Surrounds:** 4× DIYSG HT-12 (96 dB sensitivity)
- **Atmos:** 6× DIYSG Volt-10 (98 dB sensitivity)
- **Subwoofers:** 4× dual-18" sealed (Dayton UMII18-22)
- **Tactile:** 6× Crowson transducers

**Performance Targets:**
- Subwoofers: 109 dB @ 20Hz at MLP (+4 dB above THX Reference)
- Peak capability: 113+ dB @ 20Hz
- All channels exceed THX Reference (105 dB) with headroom

**Room:** 16' × 26' × 10' dedicated theater, fully treated

**Budget:** $75K-95K total investment

**Timeline:** Construction planned for 2027

